Simple Restful Service

install:
maven-3.0.4
git
sun-java6-jre
sun-java6-jdk
curl
xmllint

Tools:
--- Used to print formatted xml and json----
xmllint –format -
python -mjson.tool

STEPS:
git clone git@github.com:kidster/restfulService.git
move to project:
mvn clean install
mvn compile
mvn tomcat:run

Samples:
GET:
curl -X GET http://localhost:8080/AnonymousTcp/rest/request -H "Accept: application/xml" --verbose | xmllint –format -
curl -X GET http://localhost:8080/AnonymousTcp/rest/request -H "Accept: application/json" --verbose | python -mjson.tool
POST:
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/AnonymousTcp/rest/request -d '<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?><request><description>Test Description</description><message>Test Message</message><title>Real Title</title></request>' -H "Accept: application/xml" -H "Content-Type: application/xml" --verbose | xmllint –format -
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/AnonymousTcp/rest/request -d '{"title":"Original Title","description":"Original Description","message":"Original message"}' -H "Accept: application/json" -H "Content-Type: application/json" --verbose | python -mjson.tool
